<exercise>
<title>Sensemaking: Units of wave speed</title>
<statement>
<p>
Explicitly check the units of <m> \nu_{string} </m> to confirm its relationship holds.  
</p>
</statement>
<answer>
<p>
Let's perform a quick unit check:

<me> m/s = sqrt{N/(kg/m)} = sqrt{\frac{(kg*m/s^2)}{(kg/m)}}=sqrt{\frac{m^2}{s^2}} = m/s </me>

Indeed, the units are consistent. 
</p>
</answer>
